@startuml
title Teacher Status - State Diagram

[*] --> ACTIVE : Criar Professor

ACTIVE --> INACTIVE : inactivate()
INACTIVE --> ACTIVE : activate()

ACTIVE --> ON_LEAVE : grantLeave()
ON_LEAVE --> ACTIVE : activate()

ACTIVE --> TERMINATED : terminate()
INACTIVE --> TERMINATED : terminate()
ON_LEAVE --> TERMINATED : terminate()

TERMINATED --> [*]

note right of ACTIVE
Professor ativo
Pode lecionar
end note

note right of INACTIVE
Temporariamente inativo
end note

note right of ON_LEAVE
Licença temporária
end note

note right of TERMINATED
Estado final irreversível
end note

@enduml
